rows.label: qst106013_0010
rows.name: Internal pressure is stable, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0020
rows.name:
Dad, raise the voltage
a little more, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0030
rows.name:
Tora, isn't it dangerous to
apply any more load, mo?

rows.label: qst106013_0040
rows.name: This level is still not enough, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0050
rows.name:
We need to push it to
the very limit, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0060
rows.name:
Understood, mo. Kiku, keep a
close eye on the meter, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0070
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0080
rows.name: Alright, preparations complete, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0090
rows.name: Kiku, flip the switch, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0100
rows.name: Understood, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0110
rows.name: Now, Hana, it is time to awaken, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0120
rows.name:
Hey, hey, hey! All the lights
went out, didn't they?

rows.label: qst106013_0130
rows.name: It's pitch black, I can't see a thing.

rows.label: qst106013_0140
rows.name: Don't tell me it failed?

rows.label: qst106013_0150
rows.name: I wonder...

rows.label: qst106013_0160
rows.name:
The first time we activated Hana,
it went dark for a moment too...

rows.label: qst106013_0170
rows.name: But isn't this a little long?

rows.label: qst106013_0180
rows.name: Y-Yeah...

rows.label: qst106013_0190
rows.name: Whoa!

rows.label: qst106013_0200
rows.name: Wh-What was that?

rows.label: qst106013_0210
rows.name: W-Was that lightning?

rows.label: qst106013_0220
rows.name: Is everyone safe?

rows.label: qst106013_0230
rows.name:
...I'm fine. More importantly,
what about Hana?

rows.label: qst106013_0240
rows.name:
We did it, mo! It's a success, mo!
The birth of Hana JD Mode, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0250
rows.name: U... nngh...

rows.label: qst106013_0260
rows.name: Ah... Good morning, everyone, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0270
rows.name: Eh? Ah? G-Good morning...

rows.label: qst106013_0280
rows.name: This is the new Hana-chan...?

rows.label: qst106013_0290
rows.name:
Oh, not bad at all. Tora's
got pretty good taste.

rows.label: qst106013_0300
rows.name:
Still, she's really
grown up, hasn't she?

rows.label: qst106013_0310
rows.name: What's wrong? Jealous?

rows.label: qst106013_0320
rows.name:
...How about I make it so that
mouth of yours never opens again?

rows.label: qst106013_0330
rows.name:
Now, Hana. Let's go show
off your new power, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0340
rows.name: Roger, Master, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0350
rows.name:
H-Hey, Hana. Tora can
walk by himself, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0360
rows.name: Master's legs are short.

rows.label: qst106013_0370
rows.name:
When traveling with Hana, this is
the most efficient way to move, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0380
rows.name:
How dare you casually
insult your master, mo.

rows.label: qst106013_0390
rows.name:
Hahahaha, being held by Hana...
You look like a baby, Tora.

rows.label: qst106013_0400
rows.name: Mo-mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0410
rows.name: Tora is not a baby, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0420
rows.name:
P-Put me down, mo! Put me
down this instant, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0430
rows.name:
What's wrong with it?
It's easier that way.

rows.label: qst106013_0440
rows.name: It's not fine at all, mo!

rows.label: qst106013_0450
rows.name:
T-Tora is climbing the stairs
to adulthood... Hana! Hanaaa!
